Suchitra Krishnamoorthi's Honest Take on Attending a 'Nude Party': 'I Ran Away in 20 Minutes'

SRK's co-star from 'Kabhi Haan Kabhi Naa', Suchitra Krishnamoorthi, recently opened up about attending a 'nude party' in Berlin while enjoying a European vacation and sharing updates with her fans on Instagram. She posted about her experience, stating, "BAAPRE," and elaborated, "Just attended a body positivity/naked party in Berlin. Reminded me of the quote: don't be so open-minded that your brains fall out. Desi girl forever. Need a shower and some Gayatri mantra chanting." In an interview, Suchitra described herself as a "desi girl" and revealed that she "ran away" from the all-night party after just 20 minutes.
